name: The Orchestrator Campaign - Win USDT Rewards
description:
Imagine a compute network fueled by everyday devices, seamlessly assigning tasks to your laptop, PC, or phone. 
Each device perfectly matched to each task, by one orchestration mechanism.

But what happens if The Orchestrator vanishes?

You select all workloads, with no help at all. Here’s the lowdown:

There are no points, there is only Time. Earn it by completing tasks. 
The more time you put in, the more workloads you complete, the more Time we recognize. Simple. 

Each map brings a fresh batch of unique, one-time tasks. New maps pop every eight hours with more users, starting at 6PM UTC.

Click on blocks to start tasks. Earn time by spending time, tackling up to three tasks at once - and refer your friends to both receive a hefty bonus.
